OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FArchbishop of Canterbury   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FJustin Welby criticises    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fdelay in removing slavery  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Archbishop of Canterbury Justin Welby  
OL,6, has said the Church of England is      
OL,7, taking too long to remove memorials    
OL,8, linked to the slave trade.             
OL,10,FMr Welby criticised delays in taking   
OL,11,Fdown a plaque to slavery financier     
OL,12,FTobias Rustat at a Cambridge college   
OL,13,Fchapel.                                
OL,15,F"Why is it so much agony to remove a   
OL,16,Fmemorial to slavery?" he said.         
OL,18,FEarlier at the General Synod, the head 
OL,19,Fof a Church racial justice body said   
OL,20,Fthe lack of change was "a scandal".    
